title: Updated to 1.4
message:
Updated to 1.4

Added toggle button zoom animation.
Fixed bug where app would force close when switching from flashlight to
camera.
Added onPause and onResume activity events to better manage the camera.
Other general performance updates.

title: Update README.md
message:
Update README.md

Fixed minor grammar error and added a little link to app on Google Play.

title: Initial commit
message:
Initial commit

First commit of source code for version 1.3 of the Simple Flashlight
Android app.  Written in Java using Eclipse IDE and the Android
Developer Toolkit.
